  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Local participatory monitoring of socio-environmental indicators in the Paran&#xE1; Bo&#xE1; Bo&#xE1; IT, Amazonas</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The aim of this project is to consolidate a methodology for the use of socio-environmental monitoring tools and to build a socio-environmental profile by carrying out a participatory survey in Paran&#xE1; Bo&#xE1; Bo&#xE1; indigenous land of M&#xE9;dio Solim&#xF5;es Region - Amazonas. This will support communities and indigenous organisations to discuss guidelines for the management of socio-environmental issues that may arise in their territory and to influence local Public Policies on their land.</narrative>
  </description>
